## WEBVIEW UI DESIGN SYSTEM

### Color Palette (dark theme native)
- Background: `var(--vscode-editor-background)`
- Surface: `var(--vscode-sideBar-background)`
- Border: `var(--vscode-panel-border)`
- Accent: `#7C6FF7` (violet — NeuroCode brand, used sparingly)
- Success: `var(--vscode-testing-iconPassed)`
- Error: `var(--vscode-testing-iconFailed)`
- Warning: `var(--vscode-editorWarning-foreground)`
- Text Primary: `var(--vscode-editor-foreground)`
- Text Muted: `var(--vscode-descriptionForeground)`

### Shard Priority Badge Colors
- active file: `#7C6FF7` (violet)
- import: `#4A9EFF` (blue)
- caller: `#FF9B4A` (orange)
- memory hit: `#C97BFF` (purple) ← NEW
- semantic match: `#4AFF9B` (green)

### Review Agent Badge Colors
- architect: `#4A9EFF` (blue)
- security: `#FF4A4A` (red)
- performance: `#FF9B4A` (orange)
- test-generator: `#4AFF9B` (green)

### New Component Patterns
- GenomeConsentBanner: shown once, sticky top of Chat panel, dismissible
- MemoryNode: tree-style component, shows task → files → weight bar
- ReviewAgentCard: collapsible card per agent, colored header by type
- DriftAlert: inline warning with old/new semantic description side by side
- CausalChain: vertical timeline of stack frames, root cause highlighted red

