### Phase 1 — MVP Core (Weeks 1–8)
Steps 1–12 from original plan. See CURSOR_PROMPTS.md.
Deliverable: Working extension with Chat, Shards, Tasks, Diff apply.

### Phase 2 — Agentic Loop (Weeks 9–12)
Steps 13–16: AST graph, Planner, Task Queue, Step execution.
Deliverable: Multi-step task planning that completes end-to-end.

